biography:
Ryan Wiemeyer received his B.S. in Game Development from DePaul University. He has professional experience in production, game design, programming and UI design. His other skills range from building and starting a studio to releasing games on multiple platforms.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;

He worked for Wideload Games and put out such titles as Guilty Party for Wii and Avengers Alliance for iOS and Android. After Wideload, he formed his own studio The Men Who Wear Many Hats. Their first release was Organ Trail: Director's Cut for iOS.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;

Ryan is on the executive board of the IGDA Chicago chapter and a board member of Indie City Games.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;

